title: The Daniel Jones Era Is Upon Us, the Aging QB Fallout, and Jalen Ramsey’s Future | The Ringer NFL Show
description:
Daniel Jones, Mason Rudolph, and Teddy Bridgewater (we think) are in, and the old guys are out (1:25). Then this week's Take Shop on Eli Manning’s future, the biggest three games of the week, Cam Newton’s career trajectory, and more (31:00).
Host: Robert Mays, Kevin Clark
